nodes.text: An individual was hired by the junk dealer Watto to coordinate his largest shipment of DUM-series pit droids in the port city of Mos Espa on the planet Tatooine. At Mos Espa Circuit, Watto contacted the individual through a cam droid, asking for the pit droids to be led from their freighter, which landed in Mos Espa, to the city's podrace circuit. The contractor eventually succeeded in delivering the pit droids to the circuit with the assistance of C-3PO.
